<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><table-reference graph="None" id="_e0ca7226-e8e8-49d2-91e3-e8b1d55b891b"><num>13.2.5u</num><title id="_65b34c05-17cf-46c8-adc6-1dae8c5b122b">Masonry veneer metal-framed walls – thermal bridging mitigation</title><table id="_091ea447-f303-4ea4-bee0-f128e9824c31" keycol="1"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="001" colnum="1" colwidth="216.00*"/><colspec colname="002" colnum="2" colwidth="216.00*"/><thead><row><entry>Wall insulation <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_204c930e-8b5b-4eb2-8b13-e123d58f4285" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> from <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6397_0.23.0.xml#_89790931-1f88-42d6-ac4b-4569fb9e1815" id="_cc311b2a-2014-4b2d-bfed-53a76b297db6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Tables 13.2.5c</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6401_0.27.0.xml#_8199689d-7208-4430-9b70-e72f3728a195" id="_bc344d85-e82c-4447-bbb1-fbc38db5a541" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">13.2.5g</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6403_0.23.0.xml#_10b21ded-2b8c-4adb-a95e-0fab3b8a708d" id="_734546cb-82a5-4899-8e30-2a5886b3b531" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">13.2.5i</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6405_0.23.0.xml#_d0c70274-9298-4938-9217-b4a5145c979c" id="_39766928-5adf-4f5b-bef6-08cc660abed3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">13.2.5k</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6407_0.25.0.xml#_9cabbcb0-e87e-40eb-8ccb-f4772023dbaf" id="_194e9051-bac6-4560-b94b-fd285eda9a2d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">13.2.5m</xref></entry><entry>Thermal bridging mitigation options</entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry>&gt; 0</entry><entry>Either install <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1427_4.6.0.xml#_710062da-7211-491f-ad4c-b3f12b9b96bb" id="_2293fc17-7ae5-4adc-a1ae-85bc233c9ec7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">reflective insulation</xref> outside the frame to a minimum 20 mm reflective airspace between the frame and veneer, or add a layer of continuous insulation with an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_dede6f23-dbec-4d70-abf8-9a03c25b278e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of at least R0.30 on the inside or the outside of the frame.</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><desc-note id="_631bd371-6311-49c0-8be0-458f98203265"><ol outputclass="numbered"><li id="_89254d16-5275-4f8e-88a0-3c29b359b3b9">Minimum <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_50800a1d-2dc0-4a96-9c64-05d1826cfb5c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> are in-situ values. They account for compression of insulation.</li><li id="_83d8d511-a269-4efa-a229-a57000a15057">The surface emittance of a reflective surface facing an airspace must be a maximum of 0.1.</li></ol></desc-note></table-reference>